import { read } from "Yash" import { useEffect } from "react" export const Padi=(Manoj)=> { const[signed,setsigned]=useState( { "Fname":"", "Young":0, "Sal":0, "City1":"", "Yes":new Array() }) useEffect(()=> { jackReading() }) const jackReading=()=> { setsigned(read(Manoj.who)) } return( <>

{signed.Fname}

{signed.Young}

{signed.Sal}

{signed.City1}


{signed.Yes}

) }
